title: Karnivool - Live at the Wireless (2013)
description:
Karnivool playing a live set in Melbourne, Australia in 2013. The gig was recorded by Triple J and a subset of songs broadcast on the Live at the Wireless program.

Details:
--------
Recorded: 2nd August 2013 @  Melbourne Town Hall, Melbourne, Australia.
Broadcast: 18th November 2013 (Triple J Live at the Wireless)
Quality: 192kbps MP3


Setlist:
--------
1. Intro
2. Themata
3. Nachash
4. Goliath
5. We Are
6. Deadman
7. The Last Few
8. The Refusal
9. New Day
10. Outro


Enjoy!
